features: Houdini® Air fabric on main body and bill provides wind and weather protection with added breathability
Designed with Airshed polyester (87% recycled) side panels to dry quickly and provide breathability and airflow
The back panel acts as stash pocket for key or card and also converts to stuffsack with clip-in loop
The back panel stretches for adjustable fit and features a small slit opening for ponytails
The lightweight, moisture-wicking headband keeps sweat off your face and out of your eyes
Designed with a reflective logo for visibility when you’re running in low light
Fair Trade Certified™ sewn, which means the people who made it earned a premium for their labor
